=====Usage notes=====
The game of dice is singular. Thus in "Dice is a game played with dice," the first occurrence is singular, the second occurrence is plural. Otherwise, using the plural {{term|dice}} as a singular instead of {{term|die}} is considered incorrect by most authorities, but has come into widespread use.

